description._content: Image Description from historic lecture booklet: "The outstanding factor in the success of the Danish Fold High Schools so far has been their inspiring type of leadership. They have been capable of discussing big problems in such a way as to inspire firm and constructive action in dealing with them. One hears rumors to the effect that with the increased complication of present day problems so few of these schools are finding leaders of the necessary increased caliber that they are having less of a bearing on the live of the younger generation of farmers. Here we have a fine scholarly gentlemen who is Head Master of the Grundtvig school at Lynby."
